episodes.title: What in the Fuck Happened to Our Trailer Park?
episodes.plot: Ricky and Julian have spent another 6 months in jail, and when they return to Sunnyvale Trailer Park its a disaster. The pair inform Bubbles of their intention to start a grow op.

episodes.title: Jim Lahey Is a Drunk Bastard
episodes.plot: Ricky and Julian must ensure that Lahey wins the trailer park supervisor election over Sam Losco, a rival of the boys.

episodes.title: I've Met Cats and Dogs Smarter Than Trevor and Cory
episodes.plot: Ricky and Julian open a disco bar in J-Roc's trailer to earn the extra cash they need to expand their grow op, without tipping off Lahey.

episodes.title: A Dope Trailer Is No Place for a Kitty
episodes.plot: When the boys dope plants become infested with insects, Ricky and Julian put the surviving plants in Bubbles' shed, leading to a flaming finish.

episodes.title: The Bible Pimp
episodes.plot: A couple pretending to be a preacher and his daughter show up in Sunnyvale and look to make some cash selling Bibles.

episodes.title: Never Trust a Man with No Shirt On
episodes.plot: Randy joins the boys in their life of crime, but when they find out Randy has just been spying for Lahey, their dope operation is put in jeopardy.

episodes.title: The Bare Pimp Project
episodes.plot: Julian encourages J-Roc to shoot another porno, but it's all a ruse to make Barb dump Sam. Ricky finally gets his grade 10 and Julian sells the hash.
